Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.61,0:00:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再不赶紧的话  就要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早安  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的关心  不过今天是周日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在已经是早上10点左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有课  现在也已经迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.79,0:00:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh  no  看我都做了什么蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  回去再睡一会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:42.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉最近满大小姐傻事越做越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅是满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.19,0:00:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该说她们是变得开朗了  还是不再迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉和以前不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这果然是因为那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅是那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐也很黏着他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小莳也很喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自从风见先生来到这里后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家变得开朗起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这明明是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我却无法坦率地高兴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是也改变一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想改变这种事能被允许吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看电视吧  电视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在在浴缸里连100都无法数到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有忍耐力的孩子越来越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可以说是「宽松教育」的弊端吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  又不是我喜欢才对自己宽松的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要成为在浴缸里能数到1万的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能忍的女人事竟成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2404
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2405
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2406
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2407
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,2410
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸  饭菜要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我说了那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也知道小幸的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,注意一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得去准备些新的冰块才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我房间的冰箱里有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳菜  来帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我能叫您小雄吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸  抱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  你没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托大家的福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们担心了  真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请假？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就快考试了他不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌考试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我拿下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得要好好复习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的内容会在考试里出现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这个世界上会有考试这东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让考试消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考试啊  考试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的话  让考试消失也办的到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  别说这种荒谬的事让小幸困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是真的想她那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来发生了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后她就一直把自己关在房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手机也一直是电话留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让考试消失吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满说傻话已经是司空见惯的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照往常的话  幸也应该理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管的话  我想也不会出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过之前发生过浴室那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有些担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我之后找幸谈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给风见君办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前有没有听说过仅仅想让考试消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个女生便在学校里放了火这个事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚  发生过这样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不知道的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那件事  我就不问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一件事希望你能明确地回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会让小岭同学做出什么危险的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果发生那样的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会全力安排好  让幸和你们免受危害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你之前的事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  到时希望你能助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  由美子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.68,0:09:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:20.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须成为好孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.75,0:10:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,记得告诉小岭同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没法阻止考试
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果阿幸还是没来上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天好像很累的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以放心了  满大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被雄二叫过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被风见先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使想偷跑也是白费力气的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您误会了  我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  叫我们过来的哥哥自己却不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要不先离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是雄二还没过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…都这么晚了  不太安全吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不安全？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求各位了  快点离开这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿幸你好像很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身子还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下午都请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有事瞒着我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,B？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟平时没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你太奇怪了  小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是快回宿舍…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  你们快给我到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快  各位也快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  时间就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点啦你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃  大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧逃到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来所有人都到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在暑假前  整顿一下宿舍的纪律
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管是突然召集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位依然全部到场让我感到很欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事在宿舍做不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  所有人都回宿舍去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  幸留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我收拾一下再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.97,0:13:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是太莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给风见我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  到底是搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之后肯定会有少儿不宜的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸药…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经改造成倒计为0就停止运行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以外行的水准来说这炸弹相当不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像吓唬得有点过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了那个城市的  那个公园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了啊  小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您终于想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我到周围打听了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很幸运碰到了你的叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听他说你的父母遭遇了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家经营着一个小工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然生活艰辛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父母都非常疼爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可一旦工作繁忙起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就没空陪着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟风见先生相遇正好就是那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从您那寂寞的表情中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉到了跟自己相似的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您在一起玩耍的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我忘记了寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  您渐渐地不再去那个公园了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后那一天  10岁的生日到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  今天是你的生日  我们就休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这些日子以来让你那么寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们决定今天一整天都陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:09.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么想庆祝生日你们两个自己庆祝就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是在乱发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能原谅他们俩用寂寞两个字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就概括了我忍受了那么久的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我一个人在公园冷静下来后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才发觉到自己说的话是那么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.63,0:16:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈成了植物人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的任性  才让他们遭遇事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我必须做个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能乖乖听话的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸  我在那个城市也想起了一些自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你有听到我叫你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我当时有一点家庭烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心情很低落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过多亏了你任性地带我疯玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我心情好了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任性有时也能救人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的师父也说过这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她说一句任性话都不懂说  太老实的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让人看着就觉得心疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父母肯定也在你一直忍受着的痛苦里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想着孩子和工作究竟哪个重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最终他们得出了还是要把孩子放在第一的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是你的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是你父母所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子的任性有时也会让父母感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你再多任性一点也是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人努力到现在真是辛苦你了  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,师父还说过这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受恩不可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,受恩不报才可耻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:19:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那时的我被幸所拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那这次当是给她报恩就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在把你制作的炸药引爆销毁证据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被其他人发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经准备好了对策  把耳朵捂住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是为掩盖爆炸声而准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看看烟花也挺不错的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从那次事故之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一次都没去探望过看你母亲对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为母亲肯定憎恨着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可那天是你的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这钥匙是你叔叔给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你生日快乐  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,致幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你10岁生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你的未来是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愿你可以永远保持笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是将你的名字起为幸的我们的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱对你来说可能还有点难理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就用这句话表达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你生为我们的孩子  幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这话该我说才对  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说虽然不明显
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但确实有着恢复的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想以后多去探望一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以任性一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能请您拥抱我一分钟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一分钟就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只要这点就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回  世界树的种子I
